  schema:name "Predication hyperdoctrine" ;
  schema:description "A predication fibration that additionally supports two parallel adjoint quantifier systems — one in the knowledge order, one in the truth order — with Frobenius reciprocity, Beck–Chevalley coherence, and comprehension. The predicate-logical layer of the predication framework." ;
